WEBVTT

00:02.002 --> 00:03.294
PREVIOUSLY ON "PERCEPTION"...
WHO ARE YOU?

00:03.294 --> 00:04.925
SPECIAL AGENT DREXLER.

00:04.925 --> 00:07.838
I'M THE FBI LEGATE
AT THE U.S. EMBASSY.

00:07.838 --> 00:09.680
Patricia: IMPERSONATING AN FBI
AGENT IS A FEDERAL CRIME.

00:09.680 --> 00:11.132
WE GOT
TO FIND THIS GUY.

00:11.132 --> 00:13.134
Josiah: WE'VE BEEN WORKING
TOGETHER ON AND OFF

00:13.134 --> 00:14.895
FOR, WHAT, FIVE YEARS?

00:14.895 --> 00:17.098
YOU'RE THE SERIAL KILLER.

00:17.098 --> 00:19.730
HE SAID
HE HAD TO KILL US ALL.

00:19.730 --> 00:22.063
YOU ATTRIBUTE THIS PTSD

00:22.063 --> 00:25.526
TO THE ACTIONS OF THE DEFENDANT,
JOSIAH ROSENTHAL?

00:25.526 --> 00:28.239
YES. [ Voice breaking ]
I THOUGHT I WAS GOING TO DIE.

00:28.239 --> 00:32.703
WE'RE GETTING MARRIED
IN TWO DAYS.

00:32.703 --> 00:34.365
[ APPLAUSE ]

00:34.365 --> 00:35.916
D.J.: YOU LOVE HER.

00:35.916 --> 00:37.248
Kate: WHAT DID YOU WANT
TO TELL ME?

00:37.248 --> 00:40.661
IT MAKES ME HAPPY
TO SEE YOU SO...HAPPY.

01:01.602 --> 01:03.774
Donnie: [ Voice breaking ]
"I CAN'T DO THIS."

01:05.606 --> 01:07.148
WE'VE BEEN PLANNING THIS
FOR MONTHS,

01:07.148 --> 01:08.949
AND SHE WAITS TILL WE GET
A CHURCH FULL OF PEOPLE

01:08.949 --> 01:10.111
TO DECIDE
SHE CAN'T DO THIS?

01:10.111 --> 01:12.032
DONNIE, I'M SORRY.
THIS IS --

01:12.032 --> 01:14.575
THIS IS BULLSHIT
IS WHAT IT IS.

01:15.536 --> 01:17.077
[ SIGHS ]

01:24.755 --> 01:27.128
DONNIE...

01:27.128 --> 01:28.709
HEY, HEY, SLOW DOWN.
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

01:28.709 --> 01:29.880
I'M GOING TO FIND KATE.

01:29.880 --> 01:31.382
LOOK, YOU DON'T WANT
TO DO THIS.

01:31.382 --> 01:33.474
DUE RESPECT, JOE, THIS
IS BETWEEN ME AND HER.

01:33.474 --> 01:35.676
AND WHAT ARE YOU GONNA DO,
FIND HER AND DRAG HER BACK?

01:35.676 --> 01:37.808
NO. I'M GONNA MAKE HER
LOOK ME IN THE EYE

01:37.808 --> 01:39.980
AND TELL ME WHAT THE HELL
IS GOING ON HERE.

01:39.980 --> 01:44.485
LOOK, SON,
I KNOW MY DAUGHTER, HUH?

01:44.485 --> 01:46.227
SHE SAYS SHE WANTS
TO BE LEFT ALONE,

01:46.227 --> 01:47.648
SHE WANTS
TO BE LEFT ALONE.

01:47.648 --> 01:48.819
GIVE HER SOME SPACE.

01:48.819 --> 01:50.651
MAYBE SHE'LL COME
BACK AROUND.

01:53.734 --> 01:55.196
[ SIGHS ]

01:55.196 --> 01:58.289
SO I'M -- I'M JUST
SUPPOSED TO DO NOTHING?

02:00.581 --> 02:01.952
LET ME BUY YOU A DRINK.

02:04.705 --> 02:08.008
THANKS, JOE, BUT I'M NOT
REALLY IN THE MOOD FOR COMPANY.

02:17.178 --> 02:20.020
CAN I ASK YOU
A QUESTION, DOC?

02:20.020 --> 02:22.603
IF I SAY NO,
WILL IT STOP YOU?

02:22.603 --> 02:25.936
WHEN YOU WENT TO SEE KATE
JUST BEFORE SHE TOOK OFF,

02:25.936 --> 02:27.318
DID YOU TALK TO HER?

02:27.318 --> 02:28.979
YEAH. SO?

02:28.979 --> 02:30.321
DID IT SEEM TO YOU

02:30.321 --> 02:32.193
LIKE SHE WAS HAVING
SECOND THOUGHTS?

02:32.193 --> 02:33.574
NOT THAT I WAS AWARE OF.

02:33.574 --> 02:34.865
THEN DON'T YOU THINK --

02:34.865 --> 02:36.537
THAT IT'S NONE
OF OUR BUSINESS?

02:36.537 --> 02:39.240
YES, I DO.
SORRY.

02:39.240 --> 02:41.452
YOU NEED ANYTHING?

02:41.452 --> 02:43.454
PEACE AND QUIET.

02:43.454 --> 02:45.125
I'M GONNA GO CHANGE.

02:47.167 --> 02:48.709
Natalie:
HEY, STRANGER.

02:51.842 --> 02:55.296
NATALIE?

02:55.296 --> 02:56.927
HOW'S TRICKS?

02:56.927 --> 02:58.719
GOD, I'VE MISSED YOU.

02:58.719 --> 02:59.970
I'VE MISSED YOU, TOO.

02:59.970 --> 03:02.893
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

03:02.893 --> 03:05.726
TODAY SEEMED LIKE A GOOD DAY
TO COME BACK FOR A VISIT.

03:05.726 --> 03:07.568
I HAD PLANS.

03:07.568 --> 03:10.521
BUT AS IT TURNS OUT, I GOT
THE REST OF THE DAY FOR YOU.

03:10.521 --> 03:13.574
ONLY BECAUSE YOU SABOTAGED
THE WEDDING.
WHAT?

03:13.574 --> 03:16.076
DID YOU OR DID YOU NOT GET UP
OUT OF YOUR SEAT

03:16.076 --> 03:17.988
RIGHT BEFORE THE CEREMONY
WAS SUPPOSED TO START

03:17.988 --> 03:19.410
TO TELL KATE
THAT YOU LOVED HER?

03:19.410 --> 03:21.992
I...

03:21.992 --> 03:25.246
I HAD A MOMENTARY
IRRATIONAL IMPULSE

03:25.246 --> 03:26.587
THAT I RESISTED.

03:26.587 --> 03:28.208
SO YOU DIDN'T TALK TO HER

03:28.208 --> 03:29.920
RIGHT BEFORE SHE WAS ABOUT
TO WALK DOWN THE AISLE?

03:29.920 --> 03:32.092
YES, I DID, BUT --
WHAT DID YOU SAY?

03:32.092 --> 03:34.925
I TOLD HER
I WAS HAPPY FOR HER.

03:34.925 --> 03:36.967
BEFORE THAT?

03:36.967 --> 03:39.049
I SAID SHE LOOKED BEAUTIFUL.
SO WHAT?

03:39.049 --> 03:40.511
SO MAYBE SHE HEARD THAT

03:40.511 --> 03:43.013
AND PICKED UP
ON SOME NONVERBAL CUES --

03:43.013 --> 03:44.685
YOUR EYES,
YOUR BODY LANGUAGE.

03:44.685 --> 03:46.267
OH, COME ON, COME ON.

03:46.267 --> 03:48.899
MAYBE SHE INTUITED
WHAT YOU REALLY WANTED TO SAY,

03:48.899 --> 03:50.611
AND THAT GAVE HER
SECOND THOUGHTS.

03:50.611 --> 03:51.852
THAT'S RIDICULOUS.

03:51.852 --> 03:53.274
DANIEL, AT LEAST
ADMIT IT TO ME!

03:53.274 --> 03:55.616
ADMIT WHAT?
THAT YOU'RE SECRETLY GLAD

03:55.616 --> 03:57.448
THAT KATE RAN OUT
ON DONNIE.

03:57.448 --> 03:59.950
OKAY, YOU KNOW BEFORE,
WHEN I SAID I MISSED YOU?

03:59.950 --> 04:02.072
I WAS BEING POLITE.

04:02.072 --> 04:04.285
[ TELEPHONE RINGING ]
DANIEL, YOU'RE GONNA
HAVE TO FACE...

04:04.285 --> 04:06.957
HELLO?

04:06.957 --> 04:08.629
[ Distorted voice ]
Is this Dr. Pierce?

04:08.629 --> 04:10.961
WHO'S THIS?
I have Kate Moretti.

04:10.961 --> 04:14.965
If you ever want
to see her alive again,

04:14.965 --> 04:17.298
tell your friend Donnie Ryan
to secure the release

04:17.298 --> 04:19.139
of Dr. Josiah Rosenthal
from prison.

04:19.139 --> 04:20.761
IF THIS IS SOME KIND
OF A JOKE --

04:20.761 --> 04:23.554
Once he's free, you will
receive further instructions.

04:23.554 --> 04:24.765
You have 72 hours.

04:24.765 --> 04:26.477
If you alert the authorities

04:26.477 --> 04:28.649
or fail to deliver
Dr. Rosenthal,

04:28.649 --> 04:30.691
Kate Moretti dies.

04:40.280 --> 04:42.363
[ KNOCKING AT DOOR ]

04:46.747 --> 04:49.870
KATE DIDN'T GET COLD FEET.
SHE WAS ABDUCTED.

04:49.870 --> 04:51.792
WHAT?

04:51.792 --> 04:53.834
I GOT THIS -- THIS PHONE CALL,
WEIRD VOICE.

04:53.834 --> 04:55.676
WHOEVER IT WAS,
HE SAYS THAT --

04:55.676 --> 04:57.127
THAT HE HAS KATE

04:57.127 --> 04:59.340
AND THAT IF YOU DON'T GET
ROSENTHAL OUT OF PRISON

04:59.340 --> 05:00.551
OR -- OR IF WE ALERT
THE AUTHORITIES,

05:00.551 --> 05:01.842
HE'S GONNA KILL HER.

05:01.842 --> 05:04.725
BLESS YOUR PARANOID HEART,
DANIEL.

05:04.725 --> 05:05.806
WHAT?

05:05.806 --> 05:07.227
LOOK, I-I DON'T KNOW

05:07.227 --> 05:08.979
IF YOU'RE TRYING TO MAKE ME
FEEL BETTER

05:08.979 --> 05:10.601
OR IF YOU ACTUALLY BELIEVE
WHAT YOU'RE SAYING RIGHT NOW,

05:10.601 --> 05:13.694
BUT THE TRUTH IS,
KATE LEFT ME, PURE AND SIMPLE.

05:13.694 --> 05:14.855
YOU'RE NOT --
YOU'RE NOT LISTENING.

05:14.855 --> 05:16.106
I SHOULD HAVE SEEN
THE SIGNS.

05:16.106 --> 05:19.069
SHE DIDN'T WANT
A BIG WEDDING.

05:19.069 --> 05:20.611
SHE DIDN'T WANT
TO BUY A HOUSE

05:20.611 --> 05:22.032
OR TALK ABOUT
HAVING A BABY.

05:22.032 --> 05:23.534
DONNIE, DONNIE --

05:23.534 --> 05:25.325
DANIEL, I MIGHT BE
A LITTLE DRUNK RIGHT NOW,

05:25.325 --> 05:26.497
BUT YOU HAVE SCHIZOPHRENIA.

05:26.497 --> 05:28.499
NO OFFENSE,
BUT JUST PLEASE,

05:28.499 --> 05:31.542
ASK YOURSELF WHAT IS
MORE PLAUSIBLE HERE,

05:31.542 --> 05:37.087
THAT KATE IS BEING OFFERED
IN A HOSTAGE EXCHANGE

05:37.087 --> 05:38.509
FOR A PRISONER
ON DEATH ROW

05:38.509 --> 05:40.551
OR THAT THIS IS JUST ANOTHER
ONE OF YOUR --

05:40.551 --> 05:42.423
NO, NO, NOT -- NOT THIS TIME,
NOT THIS TIME.

05:42.423 --> 05:43.724
THINK -- THINK ABOUT IT.

05:43.724 --> 05:45.386
YOU'RE AN ASSISTANT
U.S. ATTORNEY.

05:45.386 --> 05:47.388
YOU HAVE ACCESS TO ROSENTHAL.
HE KNOWS THAT.

05:47.388 --> 05:49.229
HE OBVIOUSLY ORCHESTRATED
THIS WHOLE THING.

05:49.229 --> 05:52.272
SO YOU HAVE TO FIND A WAY
TO GET HIM RELEASED.

05:52.272 --> 05:57.398
SO WHAT, HE --
HE SENT SOME HENCHMAN

05:57.398 --> 05:58.649
TO SNEAK INTO THE CHURCH

05:58.649 --> 06:00.150
AND GRAB KATE
WHEN NOBODY WAS LOOKING?

06:00.150 --> 06:02.743
MAYBE!
M-M-MAYBE HE MADE A DEAL

06:02.743 --> 06:04.074
WITH -- WITH
SOME PRISON GANG

06:04.074 --> 06:05.446
WHO -- WHO HAD THEIR --
THEIR ASSOCIATES

06:05.446 --> 06:06.827
ON THE OUTSIDE KIDNAP HER.

06:06.827 --> 06:09.660
HE -- HE'S AN INCREDIBLY
RESOURCEFUL SOCIOPATH

06:09.660 --> 06:11.041
WHO, LET'S NOT FORGET,

06:11.041 --> 06:13.794
ABDUCTED AND -- AND KILLED
AN FBI AGENT BEFORE.

06:13.794 --> 06:15.546
AND NOW HE'S FACING
LETHAL INJECTION.

06:15.546 --> 06:17.918
HE'S DESPERATE.

06:17.918 --> 06:21.131
DONNIE,
KATE'S NOT A COWARD.

06:21.131 --> 06:24.965
DON'T YOU THINK IF -- IF
SHE WAS HAVING SECOND THOUGHTS,

06:24.965 --> 06:27.137
SHE'D TELL YOU
FACE-TO-FACE?

06:36.356 --> 06:40.861
UH, EVEN IF I HAD SOME MAGIC
POWER TO SPRING ROSENTHAL,

06:40.861 --> 06:43.193
THIS VOICE ON THE PHONE --
WHY CALL YOU INSTEAD OF ME?

06:43.193 --> 06:45.025
BECAUSE ALL ROSENTHAL
KNOWS ABOUT YOU

06:45.025 --> 06:47.287
IS THAT YOU'RE THE PROSECUTOR
WHO PUT HIM AWAY.

06:47.287 --> 06:49.329
HE DOESN'T KNOW
IF YOUR CALLS ARE MONITORED

06:49.329 --> 06:51.532
OR -- OR HOW YOU'D REACT,
BUT HE KNOWS ME,

06:51.532 --> 06:53.373
AND HE KNOWS
THAT I'D CONVINCE YOU

06:53.373 --> 06:54.955
NOT TO ALERT
THE AUTHORITIES.

06:54.955 --> 06:59.039
LOOK, MAY-- MAYBE I DID
HALLUCINATE THE PHONE CALL.

06:59.039 --> 07:01.802
BUT IF THERE'S EVEN A CHANCE
THAT I DIDN'T,

07:01.802 --> 07:03.003
YOU'VE GOT TO SOBER UP

07:03.003 --> 07:04.965
AND GO AND SEE
THAT SON OF A BITCH.

07:07.307 --> 07:10.140
[ DOOR BUZZES ]

07:13.764 --> 07:17.017
MR. RYAN.

07:20.611 --> 07:23.273
THIS IS A SURPRISE.

07:23.273 --> 07:25.736
IS IT?

07:25.736 --> 07:27.157
I ASSUMED YOU'D BE OFF
ON YOUR HONEYMOON.

07:37.417 --> 07:38.669
[ LOCK CLICKS ]

07:38.669 --> 07:39.920
HOW'D YOU KNOW
I WAS GETTING MARRIED?

07:39.920 --> 07:41.341
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

07:41.341 --> 07:43.844
MY LAWYER
IS A BIG GOSSIP.

07:47.588 --> 07:49.970
DO YOU KNOW
WHERE KATE MORETTI IS?

07:49.970 --> 07:51.351
OH, MY GOD.

07:51.351 --> 07:52.893
DID SHE LEAVE YOU
AT THE ALTAR?

07:54.094 --> 07:55.435
THAT MUST BE QUITE PAINFUL.

07:55.435 --> 07:57.518
YOU REALLY SHOULD TALK
TO SOMEONE.

07:57.518 --> 07:59.269
OFFICIALLY, I'VE HAD
TO SUSPEND MY PRACTICE,

07:59.269 --> 08:00.601
BUT I'D BE WILLING
TO SPEAK WITH --

08:00.601 --> 08:03.864
CUT THE CRAP, ROSENTHAL.

08:03.864 --> 08:07.608
DID YOU HAVE SOMEONE CALL
DR. PIERCE WITH DEMANDS?

08:07.608 --> 08:10.200
I HAVE NO IDEA
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

08:12.492 --> 08:14.665
THEN I'LL SEE YOU
AT YOUR EXECUTION.

08:16.787 --> 08:19.209
WAIT.

08:21.041 --> 08:23.624
I DON'T KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT YOUR FIANCÃ©E, MR. RYAN,

08:23.624 --> 08:26.837
BUT THERE IS SOMETHING
THAT'S BEEN WEIGHING ON ME

08:26.837 --> 08:28.799
EVER SINCE
I WAS SENTENCED.

08:28.799 --> 08:33.133
THERE ARE CERTAIN INDIVIDUALS
WHO DISAPPEARED YEARS AGO

08:33.133 --> 08:35.806
THAT WERE
NEVER ACCOUNTED FOR.

08:37.137 --> 08:40.310
I THINK ABOUT
THEIR FAMILIES OFTEN,

08:40.310 --> 08:41.852
HOW DIFFICULT IT MUST BE

08:41.852 --> 08:44.605
TO NOT KNOW WHAT HAPPENED
TO THEIR LOVED ONES.

08:47.568 --> 08:49.650
IF YOU WERE
TO CONTACT THE FBI

08:49.650 --> 08:52.112
AND ARRANGE
FOR MY TEMPORARY RELEASE,

08:52.112 --> 08:53.744
I'D BE WILLING TO HELP YOU

08:53.744 --> 08:56.156
FIND THE REMAINS
OF THOSE INDIVIDUALS.

09:01.001 --> 09:03.123
SOUNDS LIKE A SETUP.

09:03.123 --> 09:04.424
YOU SAY YOU'RE LEADING US

09:04.424 --> 09:06.376
TO THE ADDITIONAL REMAINS
OF VICTIMS,

09:06.376 --> 09:08.589
BUT INSTEAD, YOU WALK US
RIGHT INTO AN AMBUSH

09:08.589 --> 09:10.260
DESIGNED
TO HELP YOU ESCAPE.

09:10.260 --> 09:15.596
EXCEPT I DON'T RECALL
EXACTLY WHERE THE REMAINS ARE,

09:15.596 --> 09:19.439
SO I COULDN'T REALLY ARRANGE
AN AMBUSH

09:19.439 --> 09:22.522
WITHOUT KNOWING THE PRECISE
LOCATION BEFOREHAND...

09:22.522 --> 09:23.563
COULD I?

09:23.563 --> 09:25.275
MAYBE THE FBI
COULD ASSIGN

09:25.275 --> 09:27.107
ONE OF THEIR SITE
CONSULTANTS

09:27.107 --> 09:29.239
TO COME ALONG
AND HELP ME REMEMBER.

09:32.402 --> 09:35.696
MAYBE.

09:35.696 --> 09:38.118
BUT THE FBI WOULD INSIST
ON U.S. MARSHALS.

09:38.118 --> 09:40.200
OF COURSE.

09:40.200 --> 09:42.623
AND I COULD NEVER GET AWAY
FROM THEM,

09:42.623 --> 09:44.835
NOT WITHOUT HELP
ON THE INSIDE.

09:46.967 --> 09:51.341
AND WHO ON THE INSIDE
WOULD HELP ME?

09:51.341 --> 09:53.974
YOU'RE A SICK
SON OF A BITCH.

09:53.974 --> 09:55.515
AND YOU ARE A MAN

09:55.515 --> 09:58.428
WHOSE BRIDE
HAS JUST DISAPPEARED.

10:01.982 --> 10:04.434
YOU'RE RIGHT.

10:04.434 --> 10:07.397
AND I COULDN'T EVEN BEGIN
TO THINK ABOUT

10:07.397 --> 10:10.941
WHAT YOU'RE PROPOSING
UNLESS I KNEW SHE WAS OKAY.

10:10.941 --> 10:14.324
WELL, I WOULDN'T WORRY
ABOUT IT, MR. RYAN.

10:14.324 --> 10:19.409
I'M SURE SHE'LL TURN UP...
EVENTUALLY.

10:27.668 --> 10:30.010
I AM A FEDERAL AGENT.

10:30.010 --> 10:31.842
THEY WILL HAVE AN ARMY
LOOKING FOR ME.

10:31.842 --> 10:34.174
YOU ARE IN WAY OVER YOUR HEAD.
DO YOU UNDERSTAND?

10:36.677 --> 10:37.928
[ CAMERA SHUTTER CLICKS ]
UGH.

10:41.351 --> 10:44.144
JESUS CHRIST!
WHERE DID YOU GET THIS?

10:44.144 --> 10:45.686
I FOUND IT
ON MY DOORSTEP.

10:45.686 --> 10:48.478
IF WE TELL THE FBI
ABOUT THIS,

10:48.478 --> 10:49.940
THEY'RE GONNA WANT
TO TRY AND FIGURE OUT

10:49.940 --> 10:51.111
WHERE KATE'S BEING HELD
AND WHO THE ACCOMPLICE IS.

10:51.111 --> 10:53.033
THERE'S NO TIME FOR THAT.

10:53.033 --> 10:54.234
THERE'S -- THERE'S NO WAY

10:54.234 --> 10:55.946
THEY'RE GONNA GO ALONG
WITH A RUSE

10:55.946 --> 10:58.448
TO -- TO MAKE ROSENTHAL THINK
THAT WE'RE BREAKING HIM

10:58.448 --> 10:59.780
OUT OF PRISON
IN EXCHANGE FOR KATE.

10:59.780 --> 11:01.241
NO, SO WHAT DO WE DO?

11:01.241 --> 11:03.994
WE'RE GONNA HAVE TO PULL THIS
OFF ON OUR OWN.

11:06.206 --> 11:07.708
ARE YOU UP FOR THAT,
DANIEL?

11:07.708 --> 11:10.751
ABSOLUTELY.

11:10.751 --> 11:14.925
EVEN IF IT MEANS
LOSING OUR CAREERS...

11:14.925 --> 11:16.136
OR GOING TO PRISON.

11:18.218 --> 11:20.560
WHATEVER IT TAKES.
OKAY.

11:25.645 --> 11:28.769
ALL RIGHT, THE FIRST THING
WE DO IS GO TO THE FBI.

11:28.769 --> 11:30.690
WE TELL THE SPECIAL AGENT
IN CHARGE

11:30.690 --> 11:33.904
THAT ROSENTHAL IS LOOKING
FOR REDEMPTION BEFORE HE DIES.

11:33.904 --> 11:36.947
HE WANTS TO HELP CLOSE
SOME OF HIS UNSOLVED MURDERS.

11:36.947 --> 11:39.740
PARSONS WILL ASSIGN
A COUPLE OF AGENTS,

11:39.740 --> 11:42.953
BUT I AM GOING TO INSIST
THAT YOU COME ALONG.

11:42.953 --> 11:44.324
YOU'RE A PSYCH EXPERT.

11:44.324 --> 11:45.746
YOU KNOW ROSENTHAL
BETTER THAN ANYONE.

11:45.746 --> 11:47.327
YOU CAN HELP GAUGE

11:47.327 --> 11:48.919
WHETHER HE'S PULLING THE WOOL
OVER OUR EYES.

11:48.919 --> 11:51.171
PARSONS WON'T HAVE
ANY PROBLEM WITH THAT,

11:51.171 --> 11:54.714
BUT HE'LL DEFINITELY INSIST
UPON AN ARMED ESCORT.

12:00.891 --> 12:04.144
IT'S ABOUT A ONE-HOUR DRIVE
TO THE SPOT

12:04.144 --> 12:08.228
I'LL TELL ROSENTHAL TO CLAIM
HE BURIED THE VICTIMS.

12:08.228 --> 12:10.941
WE'RE ACTUALLY GOING
TO KAHAKEE STATE PARK.

12:10.941 --> 12:13.653
IT'S A PLACE THAT I USED
TO GO CAMPING WITH MY DAD.

12:13.653 --> 12:15.355
AT A CERTAIN POINT,

12:15.355 --> 12:18.618
WE'LL HAVE TO LEAVE THE CARS
AND GO IN ON FOOT.

12:21.571 --> 12:24.825
IN ORDER FOR THIS PLAN
TO WORK,

12:24.825 --> 12:27.828
WE'LL NEED TO CREATE
SOME SEPARATION

12:27.828 --> 12:30.791
BETWEEN ROSENTHAL
AND THE MARSHALS.

12:30.791 --> 12:32.632
Donnie: WHERE THE HELL
IS THIS CLEARING

12:32.632 --> 12:34.584
YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT,
ROSENTHAL?

12:34.584 --> 12:37.087
YOU SAID
IT WAS A HALF-MILE IN.
I SAID ABOUT A HALF A MILE.

12:37.087 --> 12:39.589
DRAGGING US OUT
TO THE MIDDLE OF NOWHERE.

12:39.589 --> 12:41.591
YOU KNOW WHAT?
FORGET ABOUT IT.

12:41.591 --> 12:42.933
I'VE CHANGED MY MIND.
LET'S GO BACK.

12:42.933 --> 12:45.515
NO. WE CAME
ALL THE WAY OUT HERE.

12:45.515 --> 12:47.227
NOW, SHOW US
WHERE THE BODIES ARE BURIED.

12:47.227 --> 12:48.518
IT'S NOT EXACTLY EASY TO FOCUS

12:48.518 --> 12:50.150
WITH A BUNCH OF SHOTGUNS
POINTED AT ME.

12:50.150 --> 12:52.102
THIS IS WHERE YOU COME IN.

12:52.102 --> 12:54.945
LET'S -- LET'S JUST GIVE HIM
SOME ROOM, OKAY?

12:54.945 --> 12:57.277
SIR, ARE ORDERS ARE
TO KEEP HIM TIGHT.

12:57.277 --> 12:59.109
HE'S NOT GONNA HELP US
IF HE FEELS THREATENED.

13:11.671 --> 13:14.334
EVENTUALLY,
WE'LL COME TO THE CLEARING

13:14.334 --> 13:16.756
WHERE MY DAD AND I
USED TO CAMP.

13:16.756 --> 13:18.839
THERE'S AN OLD STONE WELL.

13:20.680 --> 13:22.422
THAT'S WHERE I PUT KRISTEN.

13:22.422 --> 13:25.765
ROSENTHAL WILL GET TO THE WELL
JUST AHEAD OF ME,

13:25.765 --> 13:28.228
AND THAT'S WHEN
HE'LL GRAB THE GUN

13:28.228 --> 13:30.560
I'LL HAVE PLANTED
AHEAD OF TIME.

13:30.560 --> 13:32.232
GUN!
[ GUNS COCK ]

13:32.232 --> 13:34.734
EVERYBODY LOWER YOUR WEAPONS
OR RYAN DIES RIGHT NOW.

13:36.316 --> 13:39.109
YOU REALLY WANT TO GO HOME AND
TELL YOUR BOSSES AND THE MEDIA

13:39.109 --> 13:40.861
THAT YOU COULDN'T STOP
A SOCIOPATH

13:40.861 --> 13:42.822
FROM SPRAYING THE BRAINS
OF AN ASSISTANT U.S. ATTORNEY

13:42.822 --> 13:44.204
ALL OVER THE WOODS?!

13:45.535 --> 13:48.658
PUT THE GUNS DOWN!

13:48.658 --> 13:52.542
OF COURSE, ROSENTHAL'S GUN
WON'T BE LOADED,

13:52.542 --> 13:54.214
BUT THEY WON'T KNOW THAT.

13:54.214 --> 13:56.416
ON YOUR KNEES.

13:56.416 --> 13:58.668
HANDS BEHIND YOUR HEAD.

13:58.668 --> 14:00.010
NOT YOU, PIERCE.
GET UP.

14:00.010 --> 14:02.842
GET THE GUNS.
PUT THEM IN THE WELL.

14:02.842 --> 14:05.425
ROSENTHAL WILL ORDER YOU
TO COLLECT THEIR WEAPONS,

14:05.425 --> 14:06.726
CELLPHONES, AND CAR KEYS.

14:06.726 --> 14:09.099
COME ON, MOVE!

14:09.099 --> 14:10.730
GET THEM. COME ON.
LET'S GO. PICK THEM UP!

14:10.730 --> 14:12.893
YOU'LL DUMP IT ALL
INTO THE WELL.

14:15.185 --> 14:17.437
THEN YOU'LL CUFF
THE MARSHALS...

14:17.437 --> 14:20.740
[ HANDCUFFS CLICKING ]

14:20.740 --> 14:22.572
... AND UNCUFF ROSENTHAL.

14:24.654 --> 14:26.036
ALL RIGHT,
YOU TWO ARE COMING WITH ME.

14:26.036 --> 14:28.949
LET'S GO. MOVE.

14:30.660 --> 14:33.253
THE MARSHALS AND AGENTS
WILL TRY AND FOLLOW US,

14:33.253 --> 14:35.415
BUT IT WILL TAKE THEM HOURS...
LET'S GO.

14:35.415 --> 14:37.627
...TO COVER THE GROUND
WE CAN TRAVEL IN 10 MINUTES.

14:37.627 --> 14:39.259
THAT WAY.

14:39.259 --> 14:43.053
AND 10 MINUTES AWAY,
ON ANOTHER FIRE ROAD,

14:43.053 --> 14:45.055
WE'LL HAVE A DIFFERENT CAR
WAITING FOR US.

14:45.055 --> 14:48.638
OKAY.
NOW, GIVE ME THE GUN.

14:48.638 --> 14:51.141
WHY?
IT'S NOT LOADED, IS IT?

14:51.141 --> 14:53.223
NO.
[ GUN COCKS ]

14:53.223 --> 14:54.274
BUT THIS ONE IS.

14:56.937 --> 14:58.478
DANIEL, RELAX.

14:58.478 --> 15:00.941
TRY SOME OF THOSE BREATHING
EXERCISES WE WORKED ON.

15:00.941 --> 15:02.612
I AM NOT YOUR PATIENT
ANYMORE!

15:03.863 --> 15:05.615
WHAT HAPPENS NOW?!

15:05.615 --> 15:07.527
THE VOICE ON THE PHONE
SAID THERE'D BE INSTRUCTIONS.

15:07.527 --> 15:10.370
WE MAKE THE EXCHANGE
TONIGHT.

15:10.370 --> 15:12.292
I'LL DIRECT US
TO THE LOCATION.

15:12.292 --> 15:14.955
IN THE MEANTIME, WE GO
TO A MOTEL IN KINGSTON.

15:14.955 --> 15:16.246
WE STAY OUT OF SIGHT.

15:16.246 --> 15:17.707
NO.
WE'RE NOT GOING ANYWHERE

15:17.707 --> 15:19.169
UNTIL WE HAVE PROOF
THAT KATE IS STILL ALIVE.

15:19.169 --> 15:21.381
YOU GOT YOUR PHOTOGRAPH,
DIDN'T YOU?

15:21.381 --> 15:23.543
I WANT PROOF
SHE'S ALIVE NOW.

15:23.543 --> 15:27.887
YOU KILL ME, YOU'LL NEVER SEE
YOUR KATE AGAIN.

15:33.643 --> 15:34.724
YOU'RE RIGHT.

15:35.685 --> 15:37.187
AAH!

15:37.187 --> 15:39.609
JESUS, DONNIE,
THAT IS NOT PART OF THE PLAN!

15:39.609 --> 15:40.770
IT WAS PART OF THE PLAN
I DIDN'T TELL YOU ABOUT!

15:40.770 --> 15:42.692
[ GROANING ]

15:42.692 --> 15:45.155
I'M IN CONTROL OF THIS THING,
NOT YOU!

15:45.155 --> 15:49.699
NOW, I TALK TO KATE
IN THE NEXT 60 SECONDS

15:49.699 --> 15:51.531
OR I PUT A BULLET
IN YOUR OTHER LEG.

16:02.252 --> 16:03.423
[ DOOR CREAKS ]

16:10.680 --> 16:12.512
DONNIE: Kate!

16:14.554 --> 16:16.556
Kate, can you hear me?

16:16.556 --> 16:17.857
DONNIE.

16:17.857 --> 16:19.189
ARE YOU OKAY?

16:19.189 --> 16:22.652
I-I am. I'm okay.

16:22.652 --> 16:23.693
BUT I'M IN SOME KIND
OF A...

16:23.693 --> 16:26.196
KATE. HEY!

16:26.196 --> 16:27.527
I WASN'T FINISHED
TALKING TO HER.

16:27.527 --> 16:30.030
YOU WANTED PROOF.
I OBLIGED.

16:30.030 --> 16:32.112
[ GUN COCKS ]
I DON'T KNOW WHAT KIND
OF TWISTED DIRTBAG

16:32.112 --> 16:33.413
YOU TALKED INTO HELPING YOU,

16:33.413 --> 16:35.115
BUT IF KATE IS HARMED
IN ANY WAY,

16:35.115 --> 16:37.787
I WILL PERSONALLY KILL HIM,
AND THEN I WILL KILL YOU.

16:37.787 --> 16:39.079
THE SON OF A BITCH
WILL BE DEAD ALREADY

16:39.079 --> 16:40.830
IF WE DON'T GET HIM
TO A HOSPITAL.

16:40.830 --> 16:42.212
NO. IF WE GO TO A HOSPITAL,
THEY'LL ALERT THE POLICE,

16:42.212 --> 16:43.713
AND THIS WILL BE OVER.

16:43.713 --> 16:45.335
YOU SHOULD HAVE THOUGHT OF THAT
BEFORE YOU SHOT HIM.

16:45.335 --> 16:46.676
WELL,
YOU WENT TO MED SCHOOL.

16:46.676 --> 16:48.048
YOU SEW HIM UP.

16:48.048 --> 16:49.219
I'M NOT A SURGEON!
DON'T POINT THAT AT ME!

16:50.430 --> 16:52.592
WELL, WHY DON'T I
GIVE IT A WHACK?

16:52.592 --> 16:54.264
WHAT DO YOU SAY, JOSIAH?

16:54.264 --> 16:55.895
HOW ABOUT I DIG THAT BULLET
OUT OF YOUR LEG FOR YOU?

16:55.895 --> 16:58.558
IF I DIE, KATE DIES WITH ME.

16:58.558 --> 16:59.899
SHUT UP, BOTH OF YOU!

17:00.900 --> 17:03.563
HELP ME GET HIM
IN THE CAR.

17:06.776 --> 17:08.278
AAH!

17:19.119 --> 17:23.333
EXCUSE ME.
DO WE KNOW EACH OTHER?

17:23.333 --> 17:27.006
I DON'T THINK SO.
NO, I'M SURE
I'VE SEEN YOU.

17:27.006 --> 17:29.879
OH, MY GOD.
YOU WERE ON THE NEWS.

17:29.879 --> 17:31.971
NO, I WASN'T.

17:31.971 --> 17:33.933
YES. YOU WERE
ONE OF THOSE MEN

17:33.933 --> 17:36.346
THAT CRAZY SERIAL KILLER
TOOK HOSTAGE.

17:36.346 --> 17:38.638
IS HE WATCHING US?

17:38.638 --> 17:40.560
YOU STAY HERE.
I WILL CALL THE POLICE.

17:40.560 --> 17:42.182
NO, NO, NO. PLEASE STOP!
DON'T CALL THE POLICE!

17:42.182 --> 17:44.394
SIR?
NO, PLEASE
DON'T DO THAT.

17:48.108 --> 17:50.280
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT?

17:54.904 --> 17:57.867
YES. I JUST NEED
TO RING THESE UP.

18:01.621 --> 18:03.793
[ CASH REGISTER BEEPING ]

18:06.546 --> 18:07.917
[ GROANING, WHIMPERING ]

18:17.056 --> 18:18.718
THIS MIGHT STING.

18:18.718 --> 18:21.811
[ MUFFLED SCREAM ]

18:23.813 --> 18:26.316
IF ONLY WE HAD SOME HEROIN
TO SHOOT YOU UP WITH

18:26.316 --> 18:28.107
LIKE YOU USED
ON YOUR VICTIMS.

18:28.107 --> 18:29.649
A LOT LESS MESSY
THAN BULLETS, ISN'T IT?

18:31.231 --> 18:33.363
THE HEROIN WASN'T
FOR MY CONVENIENCE.

18:33.363 --> 18:36.326
IT WAS TO GIVE THOSE POOR SOULS
A FEW MOMENTS OF PEACE

18:36.326 --> 18:38.238
AT THE END
OF THEIR TRAGIC LIVES.

18:39.499 --> 18:41.411
THE TRAGEDY IN THEIR LIVES
WAS YOU, YOU SADISTIC PRICK.

18:41.411 --> 18:42.582
[ GROANING ]

18:42.582 --> 18:44.544
[ PANTING ]

18:47.877 --> 18:50.510
YOU MAY NOT AGREE
WITH MY ACTIONS, DANIEL,

18:50.510 --> 18:52.842
BUT I'M NO SADIST,
UNLIKE YOUR COHORT,

18:52.842 --> 18:53.963
WHO CLEARLY SEEMS
TO GET PLEASURE

18:53.963 --> 18:55.134
OUT OF WATCHING ME
IN PAIN.

18:55.134 --> 18:57.347
YEAH?
HE'S NOT THE ONLY ONE.

18:57.347 --> 18:58.388
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

19:01.060 --> 19:03.022
YOU KNOW, I'D ASSUMED

19:03.022 --> 19:07.527
THAT YOU'D EXAGGERATED
DONNIE'S CHARACTER DEFECTS.

19:07.527 --> 19:09.689
I SEE NOW THAT
YOU WERE WAY TOO KIND.

19:09.689 --> 19:12.572
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

19:12.572 --> 19:15.034
COME ON, DANIEL.

19:15.034 --> 19:17.197
HOW MANY TIMES
DURING THERAPY

19:17.197 --> 19:20.330
DID YOU BRING UP YOUR MISGIVINGS
ABOUT DONNIE,

19:20.330 --> 19:22.282
ESPECIALLY AS IT PERTAINED
TO KATE?

19:22.282 --> 19:24.123
I NEVER SAID ANYTHING
LIKE THAT.

19:24.123 --> 19:25.955
HE DIDN'T THINK YOU WERE
AN APPROPRIATE PARTNER FOR HER.

19:25.955 --> 19:27.707
SHUT UP, JOSIAH!
I MEAN IT.

19:27.707 --> 19:30.089
TRUTH IS, DANIEL BELIEVES

19:30.089 --> 19:34.294
THAT SHE BELONGS WITH HIM...
NOT YOU.

19:35.385 --> 19:38.388
[ SCREAMS ]

19:38.388 --> 19:39.929
[ WHIMPERING ]

19:39.929 --> 19:40.970
I'M GONNA NEED ICE
TO PACK THE WOUND.

19:40.970 --> 19:43.643
[ GROANING ]

19:46.105 --> 19:48.017
[ DOOR OPENS ]

20:21.801 --> 20:22.762
SOMETHING WRONG, DANIEL?

20:27.267 --> 20:29.439
I know who Rosenthal
is working with.

20:29.439 --> 20:30.810
Who?

20:30.810 --> 20:32.562
Do you remember the time
we were in Paris,

20:32.562 --> 20:34.524
the guy who -- who impersonated
the FBI legat?
Yeah.

20:34.524 --> 20:36.526
He's sitting in a car
in the parking lot.

20:52.672 --> 20:54.964
There's no one
out there.

20:54.964 --> 20:56.466
Well, he -- he --
he must have realized

20:56.466 --> 20:57.797
that I spotted him
and drove off.

20:57.797 --> 20:59.839
[ Sighs ]

20:59.839 --> 21:03.553
Isn't it more likely
you hallucinated?

21:03.553 --> 21:05.094
Hey, hey, you thought
I'd hallucinated the phone call.

21:05.094 --> 21:07.016
Daniel --
Just think about it.

21:07.016 --> 21:08.518
He's an international spy.

21:08.518 --> 21:10.730
He'd know how to orchestrate
something like this.

21:10.730 --> 21:12.522
What could he possibly have
to do with Rosenthal?

21:12.522 --> 21:13.813
I-I don't -- I don't know.

21:13.813 --> 21:15.695
But they must be
connected somehow.

21:15.695 --> 21:17.777
Maybe -- Maybe this whole
prisoner exchange

21:17.777 --> 21:19.819
is just a smokescreen
for an even bigger --

21:19.819 --> 21:21.200
Listen, Daniel!

21:23.242 --> 21:26.786
I am not sure who
or what you saw out there,

21:26.786 --> 21:29.959
but we cannot afford to let
your paranoia get us off-track.

21:29.959 --> 21:31.371
IT MIGHT COST KATE
HER LIFE.

21:32.622 --> 21:34.624
So I don't know
what you need to do

21:34.624 --> 21:36.045
to get your shit together,

21:36.045 --> 21:38.508
but whatever it is,
I need you to do it now.

21:59.739 --> 22:03.282
HEY!
OVER HERE, HEY, HEY!

22:09.038 --> 22:12.291
FEDERAL MARSHALS, SIR.
WE NEED TO USE YOUR PHONE.

22:16.215 --> 22:18.838
ALL RIGHT, PEOPLE, LISTEN UP.

22:18.838 --> 22:22.051
WE HAVE A SITUATION.

22:22.051 --> 22:24.554
Man: A MULTISTATE DRAGNET
IS UNDER WAY

22:24.554 --> 22:27.467
FOR CONVICTED SERIAL KILLER
JOSIAH ROSENTHAL,

22:27.467 --> 22:29.809
WHO TOOK TWO HOSTAGES
DURING A DARING ESCAPE

22:29.809 --> 22:32.472
FROM THE FEDERAL AUTHORITIES
EARLIER THIS AFTERNOON.

22:32.472 --> 22:34.814
SECURITY HAS BEEN TIGHTENED
AT BORDERS AND AIRPORTS.

22:34.814 --> 22:37.356
AND INVESTIGATORS ARE SAID TO
BE FOLLOWING MULTIPLE LEADS.

22:37.356 --> 22:39.068
[ SIGHS ]
JUST TURN THAT OFF, PLEASE.

22:39.068 --> 22:40.690
RELAX, DANIEL.

22:40.690 --> 22:43.072
AS LONG AS THIS PRICK HOLDS UP
HIS END OF THE BARGAIN,

22:43.072 --> 22:45.074
THIS WILL ALL BE OVER
IN A FEW MINUTES.

22:46.406 --> 22:47.487
WHERE TO NEXT?

22:49.949 --> 22:51.581
STRAIGHT TO THE END.

22:51.581 --> 22:54.253
THEN STOP THE CAR
AND TURN OFF THE ENGINE.

23:15.314 --> 23:17.356
AND WHERE IS KATE?

23:17.356 --> 23:19.649
SHE'S IN THE VAN.

23:23.402 --> 23:28.117
YOU LET ME GO, ONCE I'M SAFE,
KATE GETS RELEASED.

23:28.117 --> 23:30.580
BULLSHIT.

23:31.701 --> 23:33.703
YOU'RE NOT GOING ANYWHERE
UNTIL KATE'S FREE, TOO.

23:49.178 --> 23:50.970
[ GUN COCKS ]

23:50.970 --> 23:54.223
BRING HER OUT!
I WANT TO SEE HER!

23:58.728 --> 24:02.151
DONNIE, SHE'S NOT IN THERE.
IT'S A TRICK.

24:02.151 --> 24:04.654
DANIEL, WHERE THE HELL
ARE YOU GOING?!

24:04.654 --> 24:05.655
GET BACK HERE!

24:05.655 --> 24:07.366
YOU'D BETTER
GO AFTER HIM.

24:07.366 --> 24:08.618
AND LEAVE YOU ALL ALONE
TO JUST WALK AWAY?

24:08.618 --> 24:10.199
I DON'T THINK SO.

24:10.199 --> 24:12.952
DANIEL'S DELUSIONAL,
DONNIE. HE NEEDS YOUR HELP.

24:12.952 --> 24:17.497
MAYBE HE'S RIGHT AND THIS
IS ALL JUST A SMOKESCREEN.

24:21.340 --> 24:22.421
HEY.

24:23.923 --> 24:25.254
STOP!

24:28.848 --> 24:30.429
I SHOT HIM ONCE!

24:30.429 --> 24:33.803
I WANT TO SEE KATE RIGHT NOW
OR I'LL SHOOT HIM AGAIN!

24:44.153 --> 24:45.194
[ GUN COCKS ]

24:45.194 --> 24:47.486
KATE.
DONNIE?

24:49.368 --> 24:52.572
[ SIGHS ]
IT'S BEEN FUN, DONNIE,

24:52.572 --> 24:54.994
BUT I GUESS IT'S TIME.

24:54.994 --> 24:57.877
TAKE OFF HER BLINDFOLD
AND LET HER GO.

24:57.877 --> 24:59.749
HE DOESN'T START WALKING
UNTIL SHE STARTS WALKING.

24:59.749 --> 25:00.790
DO WHAT HE SAYS.

25:27.146 --> 25:29.358
OH, THANK GOD.

25:29.358 --> 25:30.610
ARE YOU HURT?

25:30.610 --> 25:32.071
I'M FINE.

25:32.071 --> 25:33.573
WHAT THE HELL
IS ROSENTHAL DOING HERE?

25:33.573 --> 25:36.325
I HAD TO BREAK HIM OUT
OF PRISON TO GET YOU BACK.

25:36.325 --> 25:37.707
WHAT?!
I'LL EXPLAIN.

25:37.707 --> 25:39.869
WE GOT TO GO FIND DANIEL.
HE WENT RUNNING OFF.

25:43.542 --> 25:45.294
WELL, WE CAN'T LET
ROSENTHAL GET AWAY.

25:45.294 --> 25:46.586
NO, HE'S NOT GETTING AWAY.

25:46.586 --> 25:48.547
WE HAVE A PLAN.
COME ON.

26:02.982 --> 26:04.443
[ ENGINE TURNS OVER ]

26:04.443 --> 26:06.235
[ TIRES SCREECH ]

26:06.235 --> 26:07.947
[ SIREN WAILING ]

26:20.079 --> 26:23.292
IT'S BEEN A WHILE,
DR. PIERCE.

26:24.463 --> 26:27.006
BUT WE'LL ALWAYS HAVE PARIS,
WON'T WE?

26:33.633 --> 26:35.264
IT'S PRETTY, ISN'T IT?

26:35.264 --> 26:38.217
AFTER YOU AND YOUR FRIENDS
GOT ME ARRESTED BY THE FRENCH,

26:38.217 --> 26:40.349
THEY TURNED ME OVER
TO THE IRANIANS.

26:40.349 --> 26:43.933
THEY GAVE ME THE SCAR
AS A SOUVENIR

26:43.933 --> 26:45.524
FOR FAILING TO DELIVER
THE NUCLEAR TECHNOLOGY

26:45.524 --> 26:46.776
THAT I PROMISED THEM.

26:46.776 --> 26:49.488
THAT'S WHAT THIS
IS ABOUT -- REVENGE?

26:49.488 --> 26:53.612
YOU COOKED UP THIS WHOLE PLOT
JUST TO GET US SENT TO PRISON?

26:53.612 --> 26:55.324
NOT JUST THIS PLOT,
PIERCE.

26:55.324 --> 26:57.236
YOU REMEMBER DONNIE
GETTING CHARGED WITH MURDER,

26:57.236 --> 26:59.328
YOU GETTING BLOWN UP
IN A HOUSE?

26:59.328 --> 27:01.701
IT WAS ALL ME.

27:03.332 --> 27:07.006
YOU THREE RUINED ME,
AND I'M GONNA RUIN YOU.

27:07.006 --> 27:08.337
YOU'RE OUT OF YOUR MIND.

27:08.337 --> 27:09.959
YOU AND ME BOTH.
Donnie: DANIEL!

27:13.963 --> 27:16.846
NO.

27:16.846 --> 27:18.347
DANIEL?

27:18.347 --> 27:21.020
HE...

27:22.181 --> 27:25.524
KATE, YOU'RE OKAY.

27:25.524 --> 27:27.606
ARE YOU?

27:27.606 --> 27:31.360
I'VE BEEN BETTER.
BUT YOU'RE -- YOU'RE SAFE.

27:31.360 --> 27:32.401
THAT'S -- THAT'S
ALL THAT MATTERS.

27:32.401 --> 27:33.572
WHAT -- WHAT ABOUT ROSENTHAL?

27:34.653 --> 27:38.327
[ SIREN WAILING ]

27:46.375 --> 27:47.707
[ GUN COCKS ]

27:47.707 --> 27:49.378
Joe:
GET OUT OF THE VAN!

27:49.378 --> 27:50.629
GET YOUR HANDS
BEHIND YOUR HEAD!

27:53.212 --> 27:55.134
NOW OPEN THE BACK.

27:59.058 --> 28:00.179
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATING ]

28:02.972 --> 28:05.184
JOE, WE GOT HIM?

28:05.184 --> 28:07.266
WE GOT A PROBLEM.

28:20.029 --> 28:21.911
GUY WORKS
FOR A GYPSY CAB COMPANY.

28:21.911 --> 28:24.373
HE GOT AN E-MAIL OFFERING HIM
500 BUCKS TO DRIVE

28:24.373 --> 28:25.785
AND NOT ASK ANY QUESTIONS.

28:25.785 --> 28:27.877
DID HE GET AN EYE
ON ROSENTHAL'S ACCOMPLICE?

28:27.877 --> 28:29.708
THE DEAL WAS TO PICK UP
THE VAN IN ONE SPOT,

28:29.708 --> 28:32.211
TAKE IT TO ANOTHER, AND NEVER
LOOK IN THE CARGO AREA.

28:32.211 --> 28:37.096
KATE AND I WATCHED ROSENTHAL
AND SKI MASK GET INTO THIS VAN,

28:37.096 --> 28:40.890
SO HOW DID THEY JUST
DISAPPEAR INTO THIN AIR?

28:40.890 --> 28:42.261
Drexler: IT LOOKS LIKE

28:42.261 --> 28:43.602
THERE WAS A HOLE
IN YOUR PLAN, PIERCE.

28:43.602 --> 28:44.683
HUH?

28:44.683 --> 28:46.055
TWO HOLES, ACTUALLY.

28:48.808 --> 28:49.939
DANIEL?

28:59.528 --> 29:04.864
THEY DROPPED OUT OF THE VAN
AND INTO THIS MANHOLE.

29:04.864 --> 29:07.997
SO NOW WHAT?
THEY'RE IN THE SEWERS?

29:07.997 --> 29:09.999
OR THEY CLIMBED RIGHT
BACK OUT ANOTHER MANHOLE

29:09.999 --> 29:11.290
A BLOCK OR TWO AWAY,

29:11.290 --> 29:12.631
GOT IN A DIFFERENT CAR,
AND TOOK OFF.

29:12.631 --> 29:14.463
WE GOT TO CALL THE FBI.
SLOW DOWN.

29:14.463 --> 29:17.006
WE ARE DEALING WITH A CONVICTED
SERIAL KILLER AT LARGE.

29:17.006 --> 29:18.377
WE GOT TO CALL IN
THE BIG GUNS,

29:18.377 --> 29:20.139
GET HIM BACK IN CUSTODY
AS SOON AS POSSIBLE.

29:20.139 --> 29:21.881
SHE'S RIGHT, DONNIE.

29:21.881 --> 29:23.472
WE -- WE AGREED TO FACE
THE CONSEQUENCES, TO COME CLEAN.

29:23.472 --> 29:24.643
THE FBI'S GOT THE --

29:24.643 --> 29:25.805
THE AIRPORTS
AND THE BORDERS COVERED.

29:25.805 --> 29:28.267
SO BEFORE WE CALL IT IN

29:28.267 --> 29:30.229
AND WE GET SEPARATED
AND INTERROGATED,

29:30.229 --> 29:32.982
CAN WE JUST TAKE FIVE MINUTES
AND TALK ABOUT

29:32.982 --> 29:35.815
IF THERE'S ANY WAY THAT WE CAN
FIND ROSENTHAL ON OUR OWN?

29:35.815 --> 29:37.857
YEAH, AND COVER OUR ASSES
IN THE PROCESS.

29:37.857 --> 29:40.739
KATE, IS -- IS THERE ANYTHING
THAT YOU CAN TELL US

29:40.739 --> 29:42.161
ABOUT WHO ABDUCTED YOU?

29:42.161 --> 29:44.703
I WAS IN THE CHANGING ROOM
AFTER DANIEL LEFT.

29:44.703 --> 29:47.666
WAIT.
DANIEL WAS THERE?

29:47.666 --> 29:49.748
YEAH. HE CAME IN
TO WISH ME GOOD LUCK.

29:49.748 --> 29:51.500
I FINALLY HAD A MOMENT
TO MYSELF

29:51.500 --> 29:52.671
WHERE I COULD TAKE A BREATH,

29:52.671 --> 29:53.913
AND I HEARD A KNOCK
AT THE DOOR.

29:53.913 --> 29:55.835
ALL I SAW WAS A SKI MASK.

29:55.835 --> 29:57.256
[ TASER CRACKLES ]

29:58.507 --> 30:01.380
I DON'T REMEMBER CHANGING MY
CLOTHES OR LEAVING THE CHURCH.

30:01.380 --> 30:02.882
WHOEVER TASED ME

30:02.882 --> 30:04.343
MUST HAVE GIVEN ME
SOME KIND OF A SEDATIVE, TOO.

30:04.343 --> 30:06.846
THAT SOUNDS LIKE ROSENTHAL.

30:06.846 --> 30:08.097
WHEN I WOKE UP, ALL I KNEW

30:08.097 --> 30:09.348
WAS THAT I WAS BLINDFOLDED
IN HANDCUFFS.

30:09.348 --> 30:10.729
BUT THEY TOOK A PICTURE
OF YOU,

30:10.729 --> 30:12.061
AND THEY PUT YOU
ON THE PHONE WITH ME.

30:12.061 --> 30:13.642
CAN YOU REMEMBER ANYTHING
FROM THEN?

30:13.642 --> 30:15.144
THERE WAS A LIGHT
IN MY EYES.

30:15.144 --> 30:16.936
I COULDN'T SEE ANYTHING.
THERE'S GOT TO BE SOMETHING.

30:16.936 --> 30:19.278
DID HE TALK AT ALL?
WAS HE TALL?

30:19.278 --> 30:20.609
DID HE SMELL?
NO!

30:22.111 --> 30:23.572
[ SIGHS ]

30:23.572 --> 30:27.997
I DO REMEMBER HIM
SNIFFING A LOT.

30:27.997 --> 30:30.749
MAYBE HE WAS SNORTING BLOW.
HOW THE HELL SHOULD I KNOW?

30:30.749 --> 30:32.371
LOOK, I'M SORRY,
BUT THIS IS POINTLESS.

30:32.371 --> 30:35.254
I'M CALLING THE FBI.
SOMEBODY GIVE ME A PHONE.

30:35.254 --> 30:37.336
Drexler: MAYBE YOU'VE HAD IT
WRONG THIS WHOLE TIME, PIERCE.

30:39.718 --> 30:41.460
MAYBE I WASN'T TRYING
TO PUT YOU IN JAIL.

30:43.052 --> 30:45.264
MAYBE I WAS TRYING
TO GET YOU OUT.

30:45.264 --> 30:47.676
WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

30:47.676 --> 30:48.767
WHAT?

30:48.767 --> 30:52.351
[ SNEEZES ]
AH!

30:52.351 --> 30:54.143
SORRY.

30:54.143 --> 30:56.525
THESE ALLERGIES -- KILLING ME.

30:56.525 --> 30:58.898
[ CELLPHONE DIALING ]

30:58.898 --> 31:01.480
KATE, HANG UP THE PHONE,
HANG UP THE PHONE.

31:01.480 --> 31:03.572
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]
I KNOW WHO ROSENTHAL'S
ACCOMPLICE IS.

31:03.572 --> 31:05.905
I SHOULD HAVE REALIZED IT
WHEN I SAW HER AT THE CHURCH.

31:05.905 --> 31:07.486
IT WAS RIGHT BEFORE
YOU DISAPPEARED.

31:07.486 --> 31:09.118
I-I RAN INTO TASHA.

31:09.118 --> 31:10.699
TASHA?

31:10.699 --> 31:11.951
SHE LOOKED LIKE
SHE'D BEEN CRYING.

31:11.951 --> 31:13.292
YOU BEEN CRYING?

31:13.292 --> 31:14.914
[ SNIFFLES ]
BUT NO, SHE SAID...

31:14.914 --> 31:16.085
Tasha: NO.

31:16.085 --> 31:17.546
SHE SAID
SHE HAD ALLERGIES.

31:17.546 --> 31:19.588
I-I-I ASSUMED
SHE WAS CRASHING THE WEDDING

31:19.588 --> 31:21.300
BECAUSE SHE'S IN LOVE
WITH DONNIE,

31:21.300 --> 31:23.212
BUT -- BUT SHE WAS THERE
TO ABDUCT YOU.

31:23.212 --> 31:24.763
THE TASER,
THE -- THE SKI MASK --

31:24.763 --> 31:26.385
THEY MUST HAVE BEEN
IN THE GIFT BOX.

31:26.385 --> 31:28.717
DANIEL, WHAT THE HELL
ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

31:28.717 --> 31:31.640
TASHA WAS ONE
OF ROSENTHAL'S VICTIMS.

31:31.640 --> 31:32.932
HE -- HE THREW HER OUT OF
THE VAN AND NEARLY KILLED HER.

31:32.932 --> 31:34.563
REMEMBER?

31:34.563 --> 31:35.975
I DON'T THINK HE DID
THROW HER OUT OF A VAN.

31:35.975 --> 31:37.316
I THINK SHE JUMPED.

31:37.316 --> 31:38.857
Joe: WHY THE HELL
WOULD SHE DO THAT?

31:38.857 --> 31:40.519
TO POSE AS ONE
OF HIS VICTIMS.

31:40.519 --> 31:42.611
SHE -- SHE GAVE US A WRONG LEAD,
KATE, REMEMBER?

31:42.611 --> 31:44.783
HER WHOLE STORY WAS JUST A RUSE

31:44.783 --> 31:46.865
TO THROW US OFF
ROSENTHAL'S TRACK.

31:46.865 --> 31:48.988
BUT SHE TESTIFIED AGAINST HIM
AT HIS SENTENCING.

31:48.988 --> 31:50.619
SHE HELPED SEND HIM
TO DEATH ROW.

31:50.619 --> 31:52.952
I THINK SHE WAS SENDING HIM
A MESSAGE.

31:52.952 --> 31:54.243
REMEMBER -- REMEMBER HOW SHE --

31:54.243 --> 31:55.794
SHE ASKED TO ADDRESS HIM
DIRECTLY?

31:55.794 --> 31:56.956
IT'S NOT OVER.

31:56.956 --> 31:59.498
I HAVE A FUTURE.

31:59.498 --> 32:01.130
I HAVE PLANS.

32:01.130 --> 32:03.302
THEY HAD A RELATIONSHIP.
DON'T YOU SEE?

32:04.803 --> 32:06.845
SHE WAS TRYING TO TELL HIM
THAT -- THAT SOMEHOW,

32:06.845 --> 32:08.387
SHE WAS GONNA BREAK HIM OUT.

32:08.387 --> 32:11.510
BUT HOW WOULD ROSENTHAL
GET DETAILS IN PRISON?

32:11.510 --> 32:14.143
FROM A --
FROM A, UH, GUARD MAYBE

32:14.143 --> 32:15.934
OR -- OR ANOTHER PRISONER
SMUGGLING MESSAGES?

32:15.934 --> 32:18.317
THEY KNEW THEY NEEDED LEVERAGE
TO GET YOU TO RELEASE ROSENTHAL.

32:18.317 --> 32:20.859
THEY HAD TO FIGURE OUT WHAT
WAS IMPORTANT ENOUGH TO YOU

32:20.859 --> 32:22.151
THAT YOU'D RISK EVERYTHING.

32:22.151 --> 32:24.653
SO -- SO TASHA
ASKED YOU OUT.

32:24.653 --> 32:26.735
CAN I BUY YOU A DRINK?

32:26.735 --> 32:28.737
SHE DISCOVERS THAT YOU AND KATE
ARE GETTING MARRIED.

32:28.737 --> 32:30.159
I'M ENGAGED TO BE MARRIED.

32:30.159 --> 32:32.571
A LITTLE RECONNAISSANCE
AT THE REHEARSAL DINNER.

32:32.571 --> 32:35.744
SO THEY'RE NOT GETTING MARRIED
AT ST. STEPHEN'S?

32:35.744 --> 32:37.166
NO.
THE WEDDING'S AT...

32:37.166 --> 32:38.667
AND BINGO, SHE'S GOT HER PLAN.

32:38.667 --> 32:40.079
Joe: AND NOW WHAT?

32:40.079 --> 32:41.340
YOU THINK THEY'RE RUNNING OFF
TO MEXICO

32:41.340 --> 32:42.841
LIKE BONNIE AND CLYDE?

32:42.841 --> 32:45.964
NO, NO, NO.
HE'S -- HE'S TOO SMART FOR THAT.

32:45.964 --> 32:47.926
HE KNOWS THAT THE BORDER
AND THE AIRPORT

32:47.926 --> 32:49.388
ARE CRAWLING WITH SECURITY.

32:49.388 --> 32:52.261
SO...WHAT IF HE'S LYING LOW
AT THE LAST PLACE

32:52.261 --> 32:54.853
THAT ANYONE WOULD THINK
TO LOOK FOR HIM?

32:54.853 --> 32:57.976
AT THE HOME OF A WOMAN EVERYONE
THOUGHT WAS HIS VICTIM.

32:57.976 --> 33:00.689
AW, THAT'S THE CRAZIEST THING
I EVER HEARD.

33:00.689 --> 33:02.691
WELCOME TO MY LIFE.

33:08.527 --> 33:10.529
[ KNOCK AT DOOR ]
Kate: OPEN UP!

33:11.450 --> 33:13.742
AGENT MORETTI,
WHAT IS GOING ON?

33:13.742 --> 33:16.915
YOU CAN'T JUST WALK
INTO MY HOUSE LIKE THIS.

33:16.915 --> 33:18.417
WHERE IS ROSENTHAL?
ROSENTHAL?

33:18.417 --> 33:20.119
I-I SAW ON THE NEWS
HE ESCAPED.

33:20.119 --> 33:22.251
OH, MY GOD, YOU DON'T THINK
HE'S COMING --

33:22.251 --> 33:23.922
SPARE ME THE THEATRICS,
TASHA.

33:23.922 --> 33:26.045
WE KNOW ALL ABOUT YOUR
RELATIONSHIP WITH HIM,

33:26.045 --> 33:27.676
THE MESSAGE YOU SENT HIM
FROM THE WITNESS STAND,

33:27.676 --> 33:29.178
AND THE REAL REASON
YOU SHOWED UP AT THE CHURCH.

33:29.178 --> 33:30.509
THIS IS CRAZY.

33:30.509 --> 33:32.221
I DON'T KNOW WHAT
YOU ARE TALKING --

33:32.221 --> 33:33.892
THE SECOND FLOOR IS CLEAR.

33:33.892 --> 33:35.934
NOTHING BACK HERE.

33:40.229 --> 33:42.851
I WANT YOU PEOPLE OUT
OF MY HOUSE RIGHT NOW

33:42.851 --> 33:44.403
OR I'M CALLING THE POLICE.

33:49.528 --> 33:53.992
I SAID GET OUT...NOW!

33:55.824 --> 33:58.537
[ SNIFFLES ]

33:58.537 --> 34:00.419
IT WAS YOU.

34:03.962 --> 34:05.834
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

34:05.834 --> 34:07.256
YOU LED ME UP SOME STAIRS.

34:07.256 --> 34:08.927
IS THERE A BASEMENT?

34:08.927 --> 34:10.759
YES, BUT --

34:10.759 --> 34:12.301
SHOW ME NOW.

34:38.997 --> 34:40.699
Joe:
THIS THE PLACE, HONEY?

34:40.699 --> 34:42.461
THIS ISN'T RIGHT.

34:42.461 --> 34:43.962
Tasha: I TOLD YOU.

34:43.962 --> 34:47.005
NOW, PLEASE, WILL YOU ALL
JUST LEAVE ME ALONE?

34:47.005 --> 34:49.298
3, 4, 5, 6.

34:49.298 --> 34:50.969
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

34:50.969 --> 34:53.472
I COUNTED MY STEPS TO THE STAIRS
WHEN SHE LED ME OUT.

34:53.472 --> 34:54.923
THERE WERE 17.

34:54.923 --> 34:57.476
MAYBE THIS ISN'T
THE PLACE.

34:57.476 --> 35:01.059
I HEARD A DOOR OPEN ON THE WAY.

35:01.059 --> 35:03.222
THERE'S GOT TO BE ONE
AROUND HERE.

35:03.222 --> 35:04.563
[ KNOCKING ON WALL ]

35:09.148 --> 35:11.320
Joe: CAREFUL, KATE.
NO!

35:11.320 --> 35:14.323
ON YOUR KNEES.
HANDS BEHIND YOUR HEAD.

35:31.340 --> 35:33.922
THIS IS IT.
THIS IS WHERE I WAS HELD.

35:35.804 --> 35:37.216
YOU WEREN'T THE ONLY ONE.

35:37.216 --> 35:39.258
THIS IS WHERE YOU KILLED
YOUR VICTIMS, ISN'T IT?

35:41.350 --> 35:44.523
APPARENTLY,
I'LL BE GOING BACK TO PRISON,

35:44.523 --> 35:46.525
WHERE YOU TWO FELONS
WILL BE JOINING ME.

35:47.936 --> 35:51.149
I'M CALLING THIS IN.

35:51.149 --> 35:55.234
BUT FIRST, I NEED
TO TALK TO YOU TWO ALONE.

35:55.234 --> 35:56.775
DAD, YOU GOT THEM?

35:56.775 --> 35:58.697
Joe: I GOT IT.
DONNIE, I GOT IT.

35:59.868 --> 36:01.079
COME ON.

36:06.164 --> 36:09.668
GET ON YOUR KNEES.
HANDS BEHIND YOUR HEAD.

36:09.668 --> 36:12.791
RIGHT. BEFORE I CALL PARSONS,
I NEED TO KNOW EVERYTHING

36:12.791 --> 36:15.384
THAT YOU GUYS AND MY DAD DID
TO GET ME OUT.

36:15.384 --> 36:16.795
START FROM THE BEGINNING.

36:16.795 --> 36:18.176
KATE, WHAT DIFFERENCE
DOES IT MAKE NOW?

36:18.176 --> 36:19.298
ALL THAT MATTERS
IS THOSE TWO PSYCHOPATHS

36:19.298 --> 36:21.009
WILL NEVER HURT
ANYONE AGAIN.

36:21.009 --> 36:23.141
EXCEPT FOR THE THREE PEOPLE
WHO I CARE ABOUT THE MOST.

36:23.141 --> 36:24.353
NOW, THEY'RE GONNA TELL
THEIR SIDE,

36:24.353 --> 36:26.014
AND I CANNOT BEAR THE IDEA

36:26.014 --> 36:28.517
OF YOU GUYS GOING DOWN
FOR SAVING ME.

36:28.517 --> 36:30.018
NOW, IF I HAVE ALL THE FACTS,

36:30.018 --> 36:31.270
MAYBE THERE IS SOME WAY
THAT I CAN SPIN IT.

36:31.270 --> 36:32.981
[ GUNSHOTS ]

36:35.984 --> 36:39.197
DAD?

36:40.739 --> 36:42.411
WHAT DID YOU DO?

36:45.033 --> 36:47.085
Joe:
THEY WENT FOR MY GUN.

36:47.085 --> 36:50.459
FUNNY HOW THINGS WORK OUT --

36:50.459 --> 36:54.092
TWO DEAD SCUMBAGS THAT WERE
GOING TO BE EXECUTED ANYWAY.

36:56.715 --> 37:00.218
I JUST SAVED THE TAXPAYERS
A LOT OF DOUGH.

37:00.218 --> 37:02.050
THIS ISN'T RIGHT.

37:02.050 --> 37:03.472
AND WHAT IS?

37:03.472 --> 37:05.434
ME, DONNIE,
THE PROFESSOR HERE --

37:05.434 --> 37:07.606
WE GO TO PRISON
FOR SAVING YOUR LIFE?

37:09.268 --> 37:12.110
THAT HAPPENS,
YOU'LL BE ALL ALONE.

37:13.942 --> 37:15.614
HONEY, I CAN'T STAND
THE THOUGHT OF THAT.

37:22.911 --> 37:25.163
WHATEVER WE DO,

37:25.163 --> 37:27.205
WE GOT TO MAKE SURE
WE'RE ALL ON THE SAME PAGE.

37:34.252 --> 37:38.467
THE TWO SUSPECTS CHARGED ME
IN AN ATTEMPT TO DISARM ME.

37:38.467 --> 37:40.339
IN SELF-DEFENSE, I FIRED TWICE,

37:40.339 --> 37:42.681
FATALLY INJURING
BOTH PERPETRATORS.

37:42.681 --> 37:45.384
NOW, LOOK, I WAS ALONE...

37:49.598 --> 37:52.481
YOU RUN OUT
ON YOUR WEDDING

37:52.481 --> 37:55.654
AND MAGICALLY REAPPEAR JUST
IN TIME TO SAVE THESE TWO?

37:55.654 --> 37:58.106
I KNOW HOW IT LOOKS, BOSS.
I DO.

37:58.106 --> 38:00.489
BUT I'M NOT THE FIRST BRIDE
TO GET COLD FEET.

38:00.489 --> 38:04.453
AFTER THE WEDDING, I WENT
TO STAY WITH MY DAD.

38:04.453 --> 38:05.904
WE SAW THE REPORT

38:05.904 --> 38:07.326
ABOUT THE ESCAPE AND ABDUCTION
ON THE NEWS,

38:07.326 --> 38:08.617
AND I HAD A HUNCH ABOUT TASHA

38:08.617 --> 38:10.499
FROM ALL HER CRAZY
BEHAVIOR BEFORE.

38:10.499 --> 38:12.711
SO MY DAD AND I, WHO,
AS I BELIEVE YOU KNOW

38:12.711 --> 38:14.463
WAS A HIGHLY DECORATED
POLICE OFFICER --

38:14.463 --> 38:17.255
WE FOLLOWED UP ON MY SUSPICION.
WE GOT LUCKY.

38:17.255 --> 38:20.419
IN MY OPINION,
THIS WHOLE THING STINKS.

38:20.419 --> 38:23.051
AND I DON'T KNOW WHAT
REALLY HAPPENED,

38:23.051 --> 38:25.844
BUT REST ASSURED
I AM GOING TO FIND OUT.

38:30.349 --> 38:32.310
QUITE THE IRONY,
ISN'T IT?

38:32.310 --> 38:35.063
YOU SPEND YOUR WHOLE LIFE
TERRIFIED OF CONSPIRACIES,

38:35.063 --> 38:36.695
AND NOW
YOU'RE PART OF ONE.

38:36.695 --> 38:39.358
I THINK I'LL STICK AROUND

38:39.358 --> 38:42.200
AND SEE HOW
ALL THIS PLAYS OUT.

38:43.942 --> 38:46.615
[ BELL TOLLING ]

38:50.539 --> 38:53.001
HERE COME THE GUYS.
OH, THANKS.

38:55.954 --> 38:59.588
HEY, MAX, DANIEL.
SO GLAD YOU GUYS MADE IT.

38:59.588 --> 39:02.220
WOULDN'T MISS IT
FOR THE WORLD.

39:02.220 --> 39:04.172
HEY, UM, GIVE US A MINUTE,
WOULD YOU?

39:04.172 --> 39:07.175
SURE THING.
THANKS, MAX.

39:08.887 --> 39:10.228
HOW ARE YOU HOLDING UP?

39:10.228 --> 39:13.522
MY CONSCIENCE
IS BOTHERING ME.

39:13.522 --> 39:16.605
OF COURSE, I'M USED
TO HEARING NAGGING VOICES

39:16.605 --> 39:17.896
IN MY HEAD, SO...

39:19.237 --> 39:23.402
LISTEN, DANIEL,
WHATEVER WE DID,

39:23.402 --> 39:26.405
YOU HELPED ME
SAVE THE WOMAN I LOVE,

39:26.405 --> 39:28.246
AND I WILL ALWAYS
BE GRATEFUL FOR THAT.

39:29.948 --> 39:35.874
DONNIE, I, UH -- UH,
THERE'S -- I NEED TO...

39:35.874 --> 39:38.336
THE THINGS ROSENTHAL SAID
IN THE MOTEL ROOM

39:38.336 --> 39:39.337
ABOUT ME LOVING KATE --

39:39.337 --> 39:40.919
DANIEL, STOP.

39:40.919 --> 39:43.422
THE GUY'S A WHACK JOB.
HE WAS PLAYING MIND GAMES.

39:43.422 --> 39:45.924
YES, HE WAS. BUT --
BUT WHAT?

39:45.924 --> 39:49.007
IT WAS ALL JUST A LIE,
RIGHT?

39:49.007 --> 39:52.561
NO. SOME OF WHAT HE SAID
WAS TRUE.

39:56.815 --> 39:59.277
I DO LOVE KATE.

39:59.277 --> 40:01.940
DANIEL, DON'T --
DON'T DO THIS.

40:01.940 --> 40:06.284
WHICH IS WHY I'M HAPPY
SHE FOUND SOMEONE LIKE YOU.

40:14.623 --> 40:17.205
Daniel:
ARE YOU GOOD IN A CRISIS?

40:19.297 --> 40:21.460
WOULD YOU RUSH
INTO THE MIDDLE OF THE STREET

40:21.460 --> 40:23.802
TO PUSH SOMEONE OUT OF THE PATH
OF A MOVING CAR,

40:23.802 --> 40:27.756
OR WOULD YOU DUCK OUT OF THE WAY
AND SAVE YOUR OWN SKIN?

40:34.102 --> 40:39.938
WHEN IT COMES TO CRISES,
IT REALLY DOES TAKE A VILLAGE,

40:39.938 --> 40:44.653
A TEAM OF NEUROLOGICAL NEIGHBORS
IN YOUR BRAIN WORKING TOGETHER

40:44.653 --> 40:46.825
TO AVERT DISASTER,

40:46.825 --> 40:50.659
MUCH LIKE IT SOMETIMES REQUIRES
A TEAM OF FIRST RESPONDERS

40:50.659 --> 40:54.663
TO RESCUE SOMEBODY
IN A DEADLY PREDICAMENT.

40:57.916 --> 41:01.840
WELL, WHAT IF -- WHAT IF
ALL THE PARTS OF YOUR BRAIN

41:01.840 --> 41:05.544
FAILED TO WORK TOGETHER
IN THAT CRUCIAL INSTANT?

41:13.972 --> 41:15.554
WHAT IF YOUR LIMBIC SYSTEM

41:15.554 --> 41:19.768
AND YOUR DORSOLATERAL PREFRONTAL
CORTEX BETRAY EACH OTHER

41:19.768 --> 41:22.521
AT THE MOMENT OF TRUTH?

41:59.808 --> 42:02.020
WOULD YOU SUFFER A BREAKDOWN

42:02.020 --> 42:04.983
IN THE FACE
OF WHAT SCARES YOU MOST?
